lt%20human%20body%20(or%20%22vehicle%22)%20that%20had%0Abeen%20%22prepped%22%20for%20this%20particular%20task.%20%20The%20body%20that%20was%0Achosen%20was%20called%20Jesus.%20%20The%20member%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%20who%0Awas%20instructed%20to%20incarnate%20into%20that%20body%20did%20so%20at%20His%0A%22Father's%22%20(or%20Older%20Member's)%20instruction.%20%20He%20%22moved%20into%22%20(or%0Atook%20over)%20that%20body%20when%20it%20was%2029%20or%2030%20years%20old%2C%20at%20the%20time%0Areferred%20to%20as%20its%20baptism%20by%20John%20the%20Baptist%20(the%20incarnating%0Aevent%20was%20depicted%20as%20%22...the%20Holy%20Spirit%20descended%20upon%20Him%20in%0Abodily%20form%20like%20a%20dove%22%20-%20Luke%203%3A22).%20%5BThat%20body%20(named%20Jesus)%20%0Awas%20tagged%20in%20its%20formative%20period%20to%20be%20the%20receptacle%20of%20a%20Next%20%0ALevel%20Representative%2C%20and%20even%20just%20that%20%22tagging%22%20gave%20that%20%22vehicle%22%20%0Asome%20unique%20awareness%20of%20its%20coming%20purpose.%5D%3C%2Ffont%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Ffont%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%3Ctable%20width%3D%2280%25%22%20border%3D%220%22%3E%0A%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%3Ctd%3E%0A%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%3E%20%20%20%20%20%20The%20sole%20task%20that%20was%20given%20to%20this%20member%20from%20the%0AKingdom%20of%20Heaven%20was%20%3Cem%3Eto%20offer%20the%20way%20leading%20to%20membership%20into%0Athe%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20those%20who%20recognized%20Him%20for%20who%20He%20was%0Aand%20chose%20to%20follow%20Him.%20%20%22The%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%20is%20at%20hand%22%0Ameant%20-%20'since%20I%20am%20here%2C%20and%20I%20am%20from%20that%20Kingdom%2C%20if%20you%20leave%20%0Aeverything%20of%20this%20world%20and%20follow%20me%2C%20I%20can%20take%20you%20into%20my%20Father's%0AKingdom.'%20%20Only%20those%20individuals%20who%20had%20received%20a%20%22deposit%22%0Acontaining%20a%20soul's%20beginning%20had%20the%20capacity%20to%20believe%20or%0Arecognize%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven's%20Representative.%20%20They%20could%20get%0Ato%20His%20Father%20only%20through%20total%20reliance%20upon%20Him.%20%20He%20later%0Asent%20His%20students%20out%20with%20the%20%22Good%20news%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%0AHeaven%20is%20at%20hand%2C%22%20and%20His%20followers%20could%20then%20help%20gather%20the%0A%22flock%22%20so%20that%20the%20%22Shepherd%22%20might%20teach%20others%20what%20was%0Arequired%20of%20them%20to%20enter%20His%20Father's%20House%20-%20His%20Father's%0AKingdom%20-%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%20-%20in%20the%20literal%20and%20physical%0AHeavens%20-%20certainly%20not%20among%20humans%20on%20Earth.%20%20Leaving%20behind%0Athis%20world%20included%3Cstrong%3E%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%20family%2C%20sensuality%2C%20selfish%20desires%2C%20%0Ayour%20human%20mind%2C%20and%20even%20your%20human%20body%20if%20it%20be%20required%20of%20you%20-%20all%0Amammalian%20ways%2C%20thinking%2C%20and%20behavior.%20%20Since%20He%20had%20been%0Athrough%20this%20metamorphic%20transition%20Himself%20from%20human%20to%20Level%0AAbove%20Human%20-%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20His%20Father%20-%20He%20was%20qualified%0Ato%20take%20others%20through%20that%20same%20discipline%20and%20transition.%0ARemember%2C%20the%20One%20who%20incarnated%20in%20Jesus%20was%20sent%20for%20one%0Apurpose%20only%2C%20to%20say%2C%20'If%20you%20want%20to%20go%20to%20Heaven%2C%20I%20can%20take%0Ayou%20through%20that%20gate%20-%20it%20requires%20everything%20of%20you.'%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20Our%20mission%20is%20exactly%20the%20same.%20%20I%20am%20in%20the%20same%20position%0Ato%20today's%20society%20as%20was%20the%20One%20that%20was%20in%20Jesus%20then.%20%20My%0Abeing%20here%20now%20is%20actually%20a%20continuation%20of%20that%20last%20task%20as%0Awas%20promised%2C%20to%20those%20who%20were%20students%202000%20years%20ago.%20%20They%0Aare%20here%20again%2C%20continuing%20in%20their%20own%20overcoming%2C%20while%20offering%20the%20same%20%0Atransition%20to%20others.%20%20Our%20only%20purpose%20is%20to%0Aoffer%20the%20discipline%20and%20%22grafting%22%20required%20of%20this%20transition%0Ainto%20membership%20in%20My%20Father's%20House.%20%20My%20Father%2C%20my%20Older%20Member%2C%20came%20with%20%0Ame%20this%20time%20for%20the%20first%20half%20of%20this%20task%20to%20assist%20in%20the%20task%0Abecause%20of%20its%20present%20difficulty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffont%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20Looking%20to%20us%2C%20and%20desiring%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20my%20Father's%20Kingdom%2C%20can%20%0Aoffer%20to%20those%20with%20deposits%20that%20chance%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20Level%20Above%20%0AHuman%2C%20and%20begin%20that%20transition.%20%20Your%20separation%20from%20the%20world%20and%20%0Areliance%20upon%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%20through%20its%20Representatives%20can%20open%20%0Ato%20you%20the%20opportunity%20to%20become%20a%20new%20creature%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Next%20Evolutionary%20%0ALevel%2C%20rightfully%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven.%3C%2Ffont%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%0A%3Cstrong%3E%3Cfont%20color%3D%2266ccff%22%3E%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cfont%20color%3D%2266ccff%22%3E%0AWhy%20It%20Is%20Difficult%20To%20Believe%20or%20Accept%20Us%0A%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0A%3Ctable%20width%3D%2280%25%22%20border%3D%220%22%3E%0A%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%3Ctd%3E%0A%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%3E%20%20%20%20%20%20We%20don't%20know%20if%20you%20believe%20in%20the%20real%20existence%20of%0Anegative%20or%20%22lower%22%20forces.%20%20If%20you%20do%2C%20then%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%0Aunderstand%20or%20relate%20to%20some%20of%20what%20we%20are%20about%20to%20say.%20%20It%0Aseems%20that%20how%20your%20%22programming%22%20permits%20you%20to%20see%20or%20identify%0Athose%20forces%2C%20determines%20the%20limit%20of%20your%20acceptance%20or%0Aunderstanding.%20%20Many%20believe%20that%20there%20are%20%22evil%22%20acts%20or%20even%0A%22evil%22%20individuals%2C%20but%20would%20draw%20the%20line%20before%20they%20would%0Abelieve%20in%20evil%20spirits%2C%20evil%20discarnates%2C%20negative%20influences%2C%0Amalevolent%20space%20aliens%2C%20%22Luciferians%2C%22%20or%20Satan%20and%20his%20fallen%0Aangels.%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20The%20generally%20accepted%20%22%3Cem%3Enorms%3C%2Fem%3E%22%20of%20today's%20societies%20-%20world%0Aover%20-%20are%20designed%2C%20established%2C%20and%20maintained%20by%20the%0Aindividuals%20who%20were%20at%20one%20time%20%22students%22%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%0AHeaven%20-%20%22angels%22%20in%20the%20making%20-%20who%20%22flunked%20out%22%20of%20the%0Aclassroom.%20%20Legends%20and%20scriptures%20refer%20to%20them%20as%20fallen%0Aangels.%20%20The%20current%20civilization's%20records%20use%20the%20name%20Satan%20or%0ALucifer%20to%20describe%20a%20single%20fallen%20angel%20and%20also%20to%20%22nickname%22%0Aany%20%22evil%20presence.%22%20%20If%20you%20have%20experienced%20some%20of%20what%20our%0A%22classroom%22%20requires%20of%20us%2C%20you%20would%20know%20that%20these%20%22presences%22%0Aare%20real%20and%20that%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20God%20even%20permits%20them%20to%0A%22attack%22%20us%20in%20order%20for%20us%20to%20learn%20their%20tricks%20and%20how%20to%20stay%0Aabove%20them%20or%20conquer%20them.%20%20The%20space%20aliens%2C%20or%20Luciferians%2C%0Ause%20the%20discarnate%20spirits%20(the%20minds%20that%20are%20disembodied%20at%20the%0Adeath%20of%20a%20body)%20as%20their%20primary%20servants%20-%20against%20potential%0Amembers%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20God.%20%20These%20%22influences%2C%22%20or%0Adiscarnates%2C%20are%20constantly%20%22programming%22%20every%20human%20%22plant%22%0A(vehicle%20or%20body)%2C%20to%20accept%20a%20set%20of%20beliefs%20and%20norms%20for%0Abehavior%20during%20a%20lifetime.%20%20From%20our%20point%20of%20view%2C%20this%0A%22programming%22%20finds%20that%20body%2C%20and%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20all%0Ahuman%20bodies%2C%20barely%20usable%20by%20students%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%0AHeaven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20As%20the%20above%20example%20can%20serve%20to%20testify%2C%20the%20%22lower%20forces%22%0Awould%20-%20through%20their%20%22norm%22%20concept%20-%20what%20is%20%22socially%0Aacceptable%2C%22%20what%20is%20politically%20correct%20-%20have%20you%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20believe%0Ain%20spirits%2C%20spirit%20possession%2C%20negative%20space%20aliens%2C%20Satan%2C%20etc.%0AThey%20would%20have%20you%20believe%20that%20to%20even%20dabble%20in%20these%20ideas%20is%0Aof%20the%20%22occult%2C%22%20satanic%2C%20or%20at%20the%20least%2C%20giving%20credence%20to%0A%22fringe%22%20topics.%20%20That's%20where%20they%20would%20also%20categorize%20any%0Amental%20search%20of%20Eastern%20religions%2C%20astrology%2C%20metaphysics%2C%0Aparanormal%2C%20UFOs%2C%20etc.%2C%20etc.%20%20In%20other%20words%2C%20they%20(these%20space%0Aaliens)%20don't%20want%20themselves%20%22found%20out%2C%22%20so%20they%20condemn%20any%0Aexploration.%20%20They%20want%20you%20to%20be%20a%20perfect%20servant%20to%20society%20(THEIR%20%0Asociety%20--%20of%20THEIR%20world)%20%0A--%20to%20the%20%22acceptable%20establishment%2C%22%20to%20humanity%2C%20and%20to%20false%0Areligious%20concepts.%20%20Part%20of%20that%20%22stay%20blinded%22%20formula%20goes%0Alike%20this%3Cstrong%3E%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%20%22Above%20all%2C%20be%20married%2C%20a%20good%20parent%2C%20a%20%0Areasonable%20church%20goer%2C%20buy%20a%20house%2C%20pay%20your%20mortgage%2C%20pay%20your%20insurance%2C%0Ahave%20a%20good%20line%20of%20credit%2C%20be%20socially%20committed%2C%20and%20graciously%0Aaccept%20death%20with%20the%20hope%20that%20'through%20His%20shed%20blood%2C'%20or%20some%20other%20%0Aequally%20worthless%20religious%20precept%2C%20you%20will%0Ago%20to%20Heaven%20after%20your%20death.%22%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20Many%20segments%20of%20society%2C%20especially%20segments%20of%20the%0Areligious%2C%20think%20that%20they%20are%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20%22of%20the%20world%2C%22%20but%20rather%0Athat%20their%20%22conversion%22%20experience%20finds%20them%20%22%3Cem%3Eoutside%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%0Aworldliness.%22%20%20The%20next%20statement%20that%20we%20will%20make%20will%20be%20the%0A%22Big%20Tester%2C%22%20the%20one%20that%20the%20%22lower%20forces%22%20would%20use%20to%0Aclearly%20have%20you%20discredit%20or%20disregard%20us.%20%20That%20statement%20%0Ais%3Cstrong%3E%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Unless%20you%20are%20currently%20an%20active%20student%20or%20%0Aare%20attempting%20to%0Abecome%20a%20student%20of%20the%20present%20Representative%20from%20the%20Kingdom%0Aof%20Heaven%20-%20you%20ARE%20STILL%20%22of%20the%20world%2C%22%20having%20done%20%3Cem%3Eno%0Asignificant%3C%2Fem%3E%20separation%20from%20worldliness%2C%20and%20you%20are%20still%0Aserving%20the%20%3Cem%3Eopposition%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven.%20%20This%20statement%0Asounds%20-%20to%20humans%20who%20have%20been%20so%20carefully%20programmed%20by%20the%0A%22lower%20forces%22%20-%20arrogant%2C%20pompous%2C%20or%20egotistical%20at%20the%20least%20-%0Aas%20if%20by%20taking%20this%20stand%20we%20had%20something%20to%20gain%20-%20as%20if%20we%0Awere%20seeking%20recognition%20as%20%22Deity%22%20or%20as%20self-appointed%0Aprophets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20That%20Luciferian%20programming%20%3Cem%3Ehas%20truly%20been%20effective%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%0Afor%20we%20don't%20even%20want%20to%20voice%20to%20you%20the%20statement%20in%20question.%0AHowever%2C%20believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%20it%20is%20only%20for%20your%20sake%20-%20the%20sake%0Aof%20prospective%20recipients%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%20-%20that%20we%20%3Cem%3Emust%3C%2Fem%3E%0A%22tell%20the%20truth%2C%22%20openly%20identify%20to%20you%20as%20Representatives%20of%0Athe%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%2C%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20%22fallout%22%20of%20that%0Aposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20The%20hard%20facts%20or%20bold%20statements%20in%20a%20nutshell%2C%20that%20are%20so%0Adifficult%20to%20accept%20or%20%22digest%22%20-%20come%20down%20to%3Cstrong%3E%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%20If%20you%20%0Awant%20or%20ever%20expect%20to%20go%20to%20Heaven%20-%20here%20is%20your%20window.%20%20That%20window%0Aopportunity%20requires%3Cstrong%3E%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%201)%20an%20incarnate%20(as%20human)%20%0ARepresentative%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%3Cstrong%3E%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%202)%20that%20all%20%0Awho%20hope%20to%20enter%20Heaven%0Abecome%20active%20students%20of%20that%20Representative%20while%20the%0ARepresentative%20is%20present%3Cstrong%3E%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%203)%20those%20who%20endure%20the%20%0A%22transition%20classroom%22%20until%20it%20ends%20(adequately%20bonding%20or%20%22grafting%22%20to%0Athat%20Representative)%20will%20go%20with%20that%20Representative%20-%20literally%0ALEAVE%20the%20human%20kingdom%20and%20Earth%20as%20He%20is%20about%20to%20do.%20%20Staying%20behind%2C%0Afor%20any%20significant%20period%2C%20could%20jeopardize%20that%20%22graft.%22%20%20That%20window%20to%0AHeaven%20will%20not%20open%20again%20until%20another%20civilization%20is%20planted%0Aand%20has%20reached%20sufficient%20maturity%20(according%20to%20the%20judgment%20of%0Athe%20Next%20Level).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20We%20can't%20blame%20you%20for%20%22buying%20into%22%20the%20%22Luciferian%22%0Aprogram.%20%20What%20else%20has%20been%20available%20during%20those%20periods%20when%0Ano%20Representative%20was%20present%3F%20%20Almost%20nothing%20-%20save%20some%0Awarnings%20in%20the%20Scriptures%2C%20i.e.%2C%20Luke%2020%3A34-36%2C%20Luke%2021%3A23%2C%20Mark%0A12%3A25%2C%20and%20Mark%2013%3A17-19.%20%20Check%20these%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20Another%20fact%20is%20that%20what%20someone%20is%20into%20during%20the%20time%20a%0ARepresentative%20is%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20present%20really%20doesn't%20matter%20that%20much%2C%0Aexcept%20that%20they%20are%20found%20unprepared%20when%20One%20comes%20-%20the%20only%0Atime%20when%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%20can%20be%20offered%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20The%20dilemma%20is%20%3Cem%3Ewe%20are%20here%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20most%20humans%20are%20thoroughly%0A%22hooked%22%20to%20humanity.%20%20However%2C%20the%20same%20%22grace%22%20that%20was%0Aavailable%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Representative's%20mission%202000%20years%0Aago%20is%20available%20now%20with%20our%20presence.%20%20If%20you%20quickly%20choose%20to%0Atake%20these%20steps%20toward%20separating%20from%20the%20world%2C%20and%20look%20to%20us%0Afor%20help%2C%20you%20%3Cem%3Ewill%20see%3C%2Fem%3E%20our%20Father's%20Kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20It%20is%20clear%20to%20all%20of%20us%2C%20that%20to%20the%20Anti-Christ%20--%20those%0Apropagators%20of%20sustained%20faithfulness%20to%20mammalian%20humanism%20--%20we%0Aare%2C%20and%20will%20be%20seen%20as%2C%20their%20Anti-Christ.%20%20This%20is%20certainly%0Ato%20be%20expected%2C%20and%20it%20will%20not%20delay%20our%20return%20to%20our%20Father's%0AKingdom.%20%20It%20might%20even%20accelerate%20that%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20We%20will%2C%20between%20now%20and%20our%20departure%2C%20do%20everything%20we%0Acan%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20go%20with%20us.%20%20But%20we%20cannot%20allow%20them%0Ato%20interfere%20with%20or%20delay%20our%20return%20to%20Him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffont%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%3E%0A%0A%0AThe%20Present%20Representative%3Cbr%3EDo%3C%2Ffont%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cbr%3E%0A%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ccenter%3E%3Cimg%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ccenter%3E%3Cimg%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Ccenter%3E%0AFor%20the%20next%20topic%20on%20our%20list%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%2295upd96.htm%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%0AStatement%20by%20an%20E.T.%20Presently%20Incarnate%20%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3Cbr%3E%0AFor%20subsequent%20topics%20return%20to%3A%20%0A%3Ca%20href%3D%22..%2Findex.html%23keys%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%0AHome%20Page%20Bookmarks%20%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%0A%3Cp%3E%0ATo%20Send%20Us%20an%20Email%20Use%3Cstrong%3E%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26nbsp%3B%0A%3Ca%20href%3D%22mailto%3Arep%40heavensgate.com%22%3E%20%0Arep%40heavensgate.com%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
